# Authorize HTTP layer errors (5000–5099)
E5000 = The request must use the application/x-www-form-urlencoded content type.
E5001 = The request method is not supported. Use GET or POST.
E5002 = Missing required parameters: { $fields }.
E5003 = Authentication is required for this client.
E5004 = No active session found for the requested account.
